@startuml 03_Zoom_Pipeline_Kafka
title Zoom ②③ — Ingestion CDC + Pipeline Kafka\nDe KONDOR+ à Iceberg Bronze

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam sequenceParticipantFontSize 12
skinparam sequenceMessageFontSize 11
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFF9E6

participant "KONDOR+\nSQL Server" as KONDOR #EAF3FB
participant "Debezium 2.5\n(CDC)" as DEB #E8F4E8
participant "Schema Registry\n(Avro)" as SR #FFF9E6
participant "Kafka\ntopic.raw" as KAFKA #FFE8E8
participant "StreamGuard" as SG #FFD0D0
participant "Kafka\ntopic.secure" as SEC #E8F4E8
participant "Apache Flink\n1.19" as FLINK #F0E8FF
database    "Iceberg\nBronze" as BRONZE #FFF9E6

KONDOR -> KONDOR : INSERT INTO dbo.deals\nCDM-08547 | EUR/MAD | 10M MAD
note right of KONDOR
  CDC activé sur dbo.deals
  EXEC sys.sp_cdc_enable_table
end note

KONDOR -> DEB    : CDC change event\n{op:"c", lsn:"0x0000A3", after:{deal}}
activate DEB

DEB    -> SR     : register Avro schema
SR     --> DEB   : schema_id = 42

DEB    -> KAFKA  : produce message\n{schema_id:42, payload:{deal brut}}
deactivate DEB

note right of KAFKA
  Topic : cdm.sisdm.kondor.dbo.deals
  Partition : hash(deal_id)
  Retention : 7 jours
end note

KAFKA  -> SG     : consume offset=247
activate SG
SG     -> SEC    : publish pseudonymized\noffset=247
deactivate SG

SEC    -> FLINK  : consume topic.secure
activate FLINK

note right of FLINK
  Flink Job : CDMStreamProcessor
  Parallelism : 4
  Checkpoint : 30s
  State backend : RocksDB
end note

FLINK  -> BRONZE : write Iceberg Bronze\npartition=date(2026-04-10)
FLINK  -> FLINK  : update watermark
deactivate FLINK

note over KONDOR, BRONZE
  Latence end-to-end : < 5 secondes
  KONDOR+ → Iceberg Bronze
end note

@enduml